* Norman Bethune, Canadian physician and humanitarian
* Gwendoline Kirby, matron 1950-
* H. S. Sington, anaesthetist 1907 to 1938
* Lewis Spitz, surgeon
* Catherine Jane Wood, Matron from 1880

